spec_data.Name: texlive-mdframed
spec_data.Description:
The package develops the facilities of framed in providing
breakable framed and coloured boxes. The user may instruct the
package to perform its operations using default LaTeX commands,
PStricks or TikZ.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:57:04 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Framed environments that can split at page boundaries
